text: Marcel Ackermann (born 31 July 1974) is a Swiss sport shooter. He participated at the 2018 ISSF World Shooting Championships, winning a Silver medal.300 m team rifle prone results ==References== ==External links== * Category:Living people Category:1974 births Category:Swiss male sport shooters Category:ISSF rifle shooters Category:People from Olten
